parameters: Vega has a secret treasure chest...
That box is off-limits. If you were to look inside...
Eek...! I won't look! I won't look, okay...!
It's fine if you understand. If you understand...

\SE[52] Alright, with this, Laura's part is done... \SE[3]
Next is Vita's part...

\SM[nod]\SE[2]Income... With this, it's fine. This is the
expense for weapon repairs, and this is for miscellaneous
expenses... \SE[15]... You're amazing. You've prepared the
receipts properly, haven't you?

\SE[74]... Oh. The total is off by 100G. I wonder if there's
a missing entry somewhere.

\SE[8]Ah, I made a mistake in writing Cure Life Alpha and
Beta. \. Well, let me just fix this part.......
\!\SE[7]Alright, it's complete now.

\SE[76]... Wow, you're amazing. It's already finished.
Surprisingly, you're good with paperwork... \SE[87] It
doesn't take much effort. That child...

\SE[94]So many documents...!? And they're dirty...!!
\!\SE[61]This is where the true nature of humans shows,
huh...

\SE[50]Phew... Finally finished. \. For now, I can relax my
shoulders...

\SE[74]I wonder who it is? \. Please come in. You're allowed
to enter.

\SE[3]Good job! Big sister...! I heard that you're doing
everyone's tax returns! \SE[13]If it's okay with you, can I
be of any help!?

\SE[72]Oh, Rebecca. Thank you. \SE[79]But I just finished
everything a little while ago.

\SE[14]I-Is it true that you've finished everything...?
\!\SE[37]I-I've studied how to do tax returns just so I
could be of help...

\SE[2]I-Is that so...? \!\SE[7]Well... it's fine, isn't it.
\.It'll be useful when I do my own next year.

\SE[24]I wanted to be helpful now...! I stayed up all night
studying for that... \!\SE[51]I wanted to repay the favor...

\SE[14]... I've got it! Is there anything else I can do to
help!? \SE[9] Whether it's cleaning, laundry, or anything
else, I'll do it!

\SE[2]No, there's nothing in particular that I need help
with...

\SE[66]U-Um... Well... I do a lot of desk work, so I might
have a little stiff shoulders... Maybe. \SE[80]Could I ask
for a massage or something?

\SE[15]If it's a massage, we have a professional here!! I
heard that they do it for work! \SE[14]I'll go call them
right away...!!
\SE[18]... So I brought them with me!!

\SE[2]Melissa and Lunoa...? Both of you are professionals in
massage? \SE[72]I didn't know that. That's amazing.

\SE[12]Massage, that doesn't mean what you think it does...
\!\SE[35]There seems to be a huge misunderstanding... Well,
maybe it's not entirely wrong...

\SE[14]Big sister, are you tired from shoulder stiffness? I
think you must also have accumulated stress in your daily
life! \SE[10]That's why I want you to relax and feel good
with a massage!

\SE[74]... Y-Yes, that's right. \!\SE[32](Even though I'm
not tired or stressed.)

\SE\SE[15]Certainly, I've always been taken care of, so I
want to repay the favor as well... \!\SE[15]Alright! Let me
lend a hand and help you take off your clothes....
\SE[2]You don't have to worry about things like that...

\SE[36]By the way, with Vega-san, huh... I never even
thought about it, but it's getting me fired up... \!\SE[46]I
definitely want to make you feel good.
